msgid ""
"warning **Notice** In the case of hybrid apps the ``useGlobalPipes()`` "
"method doesn’t set up pipes for gateways and micro services. For "
"“standard” (non-hybrid) microservice apps, ``useGlobalPipes()`` does "
"mount pipes globally."
msgstr ""

